{"tid":1951054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓民權領袖李多斌(妍雨)成功促使N號房更換法官","createTime":"2020-03-30T17:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T21:48:31.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cec86030f94351afb62ebaa4a0b3ad1a1671340","tid":1951054,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/b4sueh8acho21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fb4sueh8acho21.jpg&h=71325568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國網路聊天室性虐案「N號房」事件引起社會高度關注，24歲主嫌趙主彬日前遭到羈押。負責「N號房」案件的審判法官吳德植，因曾輕判對已故女星具荷拉及張紫妍等實施性犯罪的犯人，引爆40萬國民憤而連署請願撤換法官。昨吳德植疑似不堪輿論壓力，自請撤換。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/94/0e/bc/940ebc116bbd9e51f1cc39409ce9795d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F94%2F0e%2Fbc%2F940ebc116bbd9e51f1cc39409ce9795d.jpg&h=b18d1bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綜合韓國媒體報導，「N號房」性暴力事件至少有74名女性被威脅淪為性奴，其中已知的未成年少女有16人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://geeksoncoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Yeonwoo-butt-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeeksoncoffee.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2FYeonwoo-butt-1.jpeg&h=5e862091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n負責「N號房」案件的審判法官吳德植，原定昨日參與另名16歲主犯「加害者太平洋」的第一次公審。但由於吳德植輕判性犯罪者「前科累累」，許多網友擔心N號房的犯嫌無法得到應有懲罰，於是發起青瓦台連署請願撤換法官，短短幾天已經突破40萬人連署。<br />\n<img src=\"https://channel-korea.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/MOMOLANDs-Yeonwoo-4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchannel-korea.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FMOMOLANDs-Yeonwoo-4.gif&h=0e359add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在龐大民意壓力下，法院最終變更審判法官為朴賢淑（音譯）。報導指出，吳德植主動要求換人，並表示自己在擔任相關審判官時，「有明顯為難的理由」。首爾中央地方法院表示，吳德植30日已向負責分配案件的刑事首席部長法官提交申請書面資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s101.erome.com/124/F49uGbR8/KAyTGeiL.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs101.erome.com%2F124%2FF49uGbR8%2FKAyTGeiL.jpeg&h=e949fa9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9c67e8fc004edf11ebfb2c2297f08e83abef1f8","tid":1951054,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:30:10.000Z","msg":"唔準色雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cee098409217147fc9792bc37e118bedc55f574","tid":1951054,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"唔貼圖更好 咁樣幾阻礙閱讀"},{"pid":"ca73c70c0b227d66a2ea22abc08fee71903387f0","tid":1951054,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external-preview.redd.it/qldz9SJCqQT81C-t6olGK2D8v7rHqd97ZoZ84hej4hA.jpg?width=640&amp;crop=smart&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=dd98a46faf1440f1beba94dd5de8867cae66f3d7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-preview.redd.it%2Fqldz9SJCqQT81C-t6olGK2D8v7rHqd97ZoZ84hej4hA.jpg%3Fwidth%3D640%26crop%3Dsmart%26auto%3Dwebp%26s%3Ddd98a46faf1440f1beba94dd5de8867cae66f3d7&h=9fcf881d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓已故女星具荷拉，生前曾遭前男友威脅公開性愛片因而罹患憂鬱症，但當時一審法官吳德植以「影片內容重要」為由，要求觀看兩人的性愛影片。他更在判決書中詳細紀錄所有性行為的地點及次數，對具荷拉二次傷害，最後還輕判男方1年6個月徒刑，緩期3年執行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/lr88rhljnww21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Flr88rhljnww21.jpg&h=e5d4f1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已故女星張紫妍生前遭《朝鮮日報》記者性騷擾一案，也是由吳德植宣判記者無罪。此外，吳德植去年11月亦曾輕判一名曾41次拍攝女性裙底風光的李姓攝影師。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UniqueShrillCrow-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUniqueShrillCrow-poster.jpg&h=42b4e5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200331/4AKIA45T4WKSQ5DQXLK6FGNA4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200331%2F4AKIA45T4WKSQ5DQXLK6FGNA4I%2F&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=e1a019e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200331%2F4AKIA45T4WKSQ5DQXLK6FGNA4I%2F&h=5cf5c9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200331/4AKIA45T4WKSQ5DQXLK6FGNA4I/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s101.erome.com/124/F49uGbR8/HK74X6cY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs101.erome.com%2F124%2FF49uGbR8%2FHK74X6cY.jpeg&h=4dfa150f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考：參加N號房請願遭酸「高中學歷的戲子」 妍雨高EQ反擊：身為人該有的是非判斷力<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1678984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1678984&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=49f9640a\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1678984</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vPwHS5N8irA/W8u7i8JtVlI/AAAAAAACZDQ/Ax34jy0Ov8k8lBZ5tYxNvMFCMjfiskLLwCLcBGAs/s1600/yeonwoo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-vPwHS5N8irA%2FW8u7i8JtVlI%2FAAAAAAACZDQ%2FAx34jy0Ov8k8lBZ5tYxNvMFCMjfiskLLwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fyeonwoo.jpg&h=44ac68b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2c2a884f7376d6434f1a6ed4232227efa14ced8","tid":1951054,"uid":34241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"妍雨人都走左<br />\n唔好搞人啦"},{"pid":"bf277fd6df129c4b493b4a3d6ae7a5be42ec70c2","tid":1951054,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9c67e8fc004edf11ebfb2c2297f08e83abef1f8","tid":1951054,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:30:10.000Z","msg":"唔準色雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"654f2f0da5f369c019fba47b8d736862aa34d74c","tid":1951054,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"佢之前有段時間有panic disorder<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3afb577cfbde55cd5f86463b37989a2541804d0","tid":1951054,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re